              <span class="d-block font-italic">(Clostridium leptum) </span>
              <span class="d-block">促進短鏈脂肪酸生成、提供腸道細胞能量，抑制壞菌。 </span>
              <div class="bacteriaScore-container text-center">
                <span class="bacteriaScore">一般</span>
              </div>
            </li>
          </ul>
